main event: A report related to sightings of unidentified flying objects in western Montana in April 1965.
interesting points: The report originated from an unknown source,The individual who submitted the report claims to have had sightings since the original incident but is now over 80 years old,There were multiple sightings of fantastic flying objects reported by individuals in the area,The objects were described as being as big as an airplane, brightly lighted, and flying swiftly without any sound,The photos related to the evaluations were requested but were not received.
